content.value: In this video, Contentful's Liz Osterloh takes you for a spin around Compose, Contentful's new app for editors to create pages and manage content. Compose gives editors a sleeker and more page-centric interface while structured content still works its magic under the hood, letting you create content once and publish it anywhere.
